INSTITUTE  (1USALRL)
REFERENCE  (J,PR,122,164,1961)
           #doi:10.1103/PhysRev.122.164
AUTHOR     (M.D.Goldberg,J.M.Le Blanc)
TITLE      Angular Yield of Neutrons from the T(d,n)He4 Reaction
             for 6- to 11.5-MeV Neutrons
FACILITY   (CYCLO,1USALRL) 90-inch variable energy cyclotron
SAMPLE     One atmosphere of Tritium gas of unknown purity in a
             stainless steel gas cell 4 inches in length by 1-inch
             in diameter.  10 mg/cm2 Ta entrance foil and 0.020-
             inch Ta beam stopper.
DETECTOR   (TELES) Similar to proton-recoil telescope described in
             Phys.Rev.119,1992 (1960).
ERR-ANALYS (EN-ERR) Determined to be 2% by a differential range
            measurement.
REL-REF    (I,C0043001,M.D.Goldberg+,J,PR,119,1992,1960)
            Description of proton-recoil telescope and of
            the method used to determine the uncertainty in
            the incident beam energy.
HISTORY    (19790110C)TWB
           (19800305A)TWB
           (19960222A) BIB Corrections, converted to lower case.
           (20020213A) Converted to new date formats.
           (20260111A) OS. ANG-ERR moved to subs.2-4, STATUS,
            ERR-ANALYS updated, BIB updates
